      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒生银行将2023年中国房地产投资削减33%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/hang-seng-bank-slashes-china-property-exposure-by-33-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[恒生银行去年将其中国大陆商业房地产风险敞口削减了三分之一，以降低陷入困境的行业的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/hang-seng-bank-slashes-china-property-exposure-by-33-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:14:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行首席执行官奎因：尽管交通银行收取30亿美元费用，但对中国“充满信心”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-21/hsbc-s-quinn-have-strong-confidence-in-china-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行首席执行官诺埃尔·奎因 (Noel Quinn) 谈到该银行史无前例地对其持有的中国交通银行股份收取 30 亿美元费用。我还想重申，我们对中国经济充满信心。”奎因在接受彭博电视台采访时谈到交通银行的指控时表示。他发表此番言论之前，汇丰银行宣布去年最后三个月税前利润从上年同期的 50.5 亿美元降至 10 亿美元。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-21/hsbc-s-quinn-have-strong-confidence-in-china-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着能源危机消退，嘉能可利润大幅下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/glencore-posts-steep-profit-fall-as-energy-crisis-fades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司(Glencore Plc)报告称，在市场从俄罗斯入侵乌克兰后带来巨额盈利的价格飙升和剧烈波动中回落后，利润急剧下降，并降低了股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/glencore-posts-steep-profit-fall-as-energy-crisis-fades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>费森尤斯的目标是通过削减成本实现更快的盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/fresenius-targets-faster-earnings-growth-after-more-cost-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费森尤斯公司预计，由于更多的成本削减措施和对其静脉注射药物的强劲需求，今年的盈利增长将更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/fresenius-targets-faster-earnings-growth-after-more-cost-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 06:10:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着支持措施的增加，中国股市跃升至数周最高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/china-stocks-rally-on-quant-fund-clampdown-property-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着当局打压量化基金交易，中国股市上涨，这是一系列旨在结束股市暴跌的努力中的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/china-stocks-rally-on-quant-fund-clampdown-property-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 03:50:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于供应紧张和需求担忧，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国股市上涨的提振，油价小幅走高，投资者在供应紧张的迹象、中东紧张局势加剧以及需求前景依然不稳定之间进行权衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-21</guid>
